as Member of the [[Vidhan Sabha|Legislative Assembly]] from [[Osmanabad (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Osmanabad Vidhan Sabha constituency]] of [[Osmanabad District]], [[Maharashtra]], India as a member of [[Shiv Sena]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elections.in/maharashtra/assembly-constituencies/osmanabad.html|title=Osmanabad (Maharashtra) Election Results 2014, Current and Previous MLA|work=elections.in|access-date=18 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118143235/http://www.elections.in/maharashtra/assembly-constituencies/osmanabad.html#|archive-date=18 November 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n==Positions held==\n* 2009: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly\n* 2019: Elected to 17th Lok Sabha <ref>{{cite web | url=https://abpmajha.abplive.in/maharashtra/loksabha-election-results-2019-winning-candidate-list-of-maharashtra-667510| title=Loksabha Election Results 2019 : \u0930\u093e\u091c\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0924\u0940\u0932 \u0935\u093f\u091c\u092f\u0940 \u0909\u092e\u0947\u0926\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e\u0902\u091a\u0940 \u092f\u093e\u0926\u0940}}</ref>\n==See also==\n* [[Osmanabad Tahsil|Osmanabad Taluka]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.shivsena.org/ Shivsena Home Page]\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rajenimbalkar, Omprakash}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Shiv Sena politicians]]\n[[Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2009\u20132014]]\n[[Category:People from Osmanabad district]]\n[[Category:Marathi politicians]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2017}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2017}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| honorific-prefix    = \n| name                = Omprakash Raje Nimbalkar\n| image               = \n| office              = Member of Parliament, Lok Sabha\n| term_start          = 2019\n| term_end            = \n| constituency        = [[Osmanabad (Lok Sabha constituency) | Osmanabad]]\n| office1             = [[Maharashtra Legi